  <title class="- topic/title ">Behavioral Targeting Basic Steps</title>
  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">The following steps outline the process
	 of setting up behavioral targeting. 
  </shortdesc>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <othermeta name="solution" content="Target" />
      <othermeta name="topic" content="Advanced" />
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <refbody class="- topic/body        reference/refbody ">
    <refsyn id="refsyn_2672884A5E4C42E698C9379006CBABD2" class="- topic/section     reference/refsyn ">
      <p class="- topic/p ">
        <ol id="ol_5EBF2FE1C83C4680ACDD8AC1E5FC54C3" class="- topic/ol ">
          <li id="li_1C53AE6B55F340E59B4362A9AD07E15E" class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Define your business objective. 
			 </p>
            <p class="- topic/p ">
              <ul id="ul_9EFAB81E680A44D6AA351B54FEF5E147" class="- topic/ul ">
                <li id="li_F36FA74575E041FF911459E9741AB83F" class="- topic/li ">
				  Clear out old inventory? 
				</li>
                <li id="li_8A2D45F1CD7940A79D9BAC8F152B5AD9" class="- topic/li ">
				  Highlight a niche product? 
				</li>
                <li id="li_3FE3752C599846CF9BE669A6FEFEBB92" class="- topic/li ">
				  Increase form completion from female visitors? 
				</li>
                <li id="li_51332B9E959546E29E21F299A457C587" class="- topic/li ">
				  Map your customer segmentation to your Web content. 
				</li>
              </ul>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li id="li_F703493793A742BEBE6965331E76224E" class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Define the user most likely to help you. 
			 </p>
            <p class="- topic/p ">
              <ul id="ul_6481F350CEBD49839B2B934FFB6803B0" class="- topic/ul ">
                <li id="li_34CBB1C65A9949DCB96E894293F90B4D" class="- topic/li ">
				  Who are these people? 
				</li>
                <li id="li_2735D08448A64427B2BE265FDA2B7886" class="- topic/li ">
				  Start with simple, broad segments and refine them over time. 
				</li>
              </ul>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li id="li_622C0FF4C5B442058AF8B9F1DB5BF9DC" class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Define the behaviors the user is most likely to
				exhibit. 
			 </p>
            <p class="- topic/p ">
              <ul id="ul_1E15D90F9B674BE3B206145FDF8A55E3" class="- topic/ul ">
                <li id="li_7E36375CD21D443FBCD37AF0E4551CBC" class="- topic/li ">
				  Are they a return visitor? 
				</li>
                <li id="li_40C189A31509437EA9A67CD1B22B7156" class="- topic/li ">
				  Are they a frequent visitor? 
				</li>
                <li id="li_B935FB7762B547BB90CE39B78C5E0CD9" class="- topic/li ">
				  What pages do they visit? 
				</li>
                <li id="li_E5FEF145131141CFAAB7AAD2A765E9FD" class="- topic/li ">
				  Have they filled out a form before? 
				</li>
                <li id="li_4A0F27DC4F1741C6B2ED942725976ABF" class="- topic/li ">
				  Have they purchased something before? 
				</li>
                <li id="li_05EE27F7DD714EFAB5011A80FD6B6293" class="- topic/li ">
				  Are they weekend shoppers? 
				</li>
                <li id="li_08430446E6F245418B430B7C8BF76370" class="- topic/li ">
				  Did they come from specific search engines? Social referrers? 
				</li>
                <li id="li_AB06A9E4ACC341EE821DE5B475D1D176" class="- topic/li ">
				  Do they come primarily from certain geographies? 
				</li>
              </ul>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li id="li_1AB86AAEE5AE4A689F6E8FA8E823A9D7" class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Capture relevant behaviors in profiles. 
			 </p>
            <p class="- topic/p ">
              <ul id="ul_89F87BEEEDD14C40AC9CFA6FA0B52552" class="- topic/ul ">
                <li id="li_E01C7D9A714B415B8332B463CEA0988F" class="- topic/li ">
				  Custom created labels for your users 
				</li>
                <li id="li_457AC2089B1B4DEAB08A03470B4E66A7" class="- topic/li ">
				  Stored in databases and associated with your visitor through a cookie 
				</li>
                <li id="li_EF2325828AC644BC8C4A2EA948F99DF0" class="- topic/li ">
				  Two strategies: either 
				  <xref href="c_Profile_Parameters.xml#concept_01A30B4762D64CD5946B3AA38DC8A201" type="concept" format="dita" scope="local" class="- topic/xref ">in-mbox
					 profile parameters or script profile parameters</xref></li>
                <li id="li_8941400E179E47F889D876BF6B1EC891" class="- topic/li ">
				  In-mbox profile parameters are placed in the page's mboxCreate call: 
				  <p class="- topic/p "><codeblock outputclass="syntax html">&lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt;

   mboxCreate('myMbox', 'profile.name1=value1', 'profile.name2=value2');

&lt;/script&gt;

&lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt; mboxCreate('myMbox',

'profile.name1=value1', 'profile.name2=value2'); &lt;/script&gt;</codeblock></p></li>
                <li id="li_24E3CE9E57254F4FB12A301987E38E7A" class="- topic/li ">
				  Script profile parameters are defined with JavaScript in the admin tool: 
				  <ol id="ol_2AD9F8E27C1C4EB6A0DD966F879EE718" class="- topic/ol "><li id="li_6D46EA9F5CD4438986D873260F192891" class="- topic/li "> Select 
						<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Segments</uicontrol> &gt; 
						<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Profiles</uicontrol>. 
						<p class="- topic/p "></p></li><li id="li_4020EB3C797244418313FE657E6C3825" class="- topic/li "> Clicking 
						<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">add
						  attribute</uicontrol> to add a new parameter. 
					 </li><li id="li_9913A4E9A63843C2A92AA1E17FA735D1" class="- topic/li "> Name your profile and type the JavaScript code into the
						text fields. 
						<p class="- topic/p "></p></li><li id="li_0ACC7948A8F4437184B136BE7F853392" class="- topic/li "> Click 
						<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Start</uicontrol> to start the script. 
					 </li></ol><p class="- topic/p ">The profile data is now available for use
					 in campaigns. 
				  </p></li>
              </ul>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li id="li_90F16165618047629AFB8A902F83D025" class="- topic/li ">
			 Target content to those users based on their profiles. 
			 <ul id="ul_DF1F3D6949DE49EDAF6FC9A8C482E539" class="- topic/ul "><li id="li_6B772F33672849B382CD1121AEBE12CE" class="- topic/li ">
				  Create offers and use the 
				  <xref href="c_Targeting_a_Campaign_or_Test.xml#concept_A782F8481A5041EBA75103CB26376522" type="concept" format="dita" scope="local" class="- topic/xref ">targeting
					 features</xref> to send that content to specific users. 
				</li></ul></li>
        </ol>
      </p>
    </refsyn>
